OL,7,FPolice have released footage of the
OL,8,Fchilling moment a dog walker screamed
OL,9,Fas she witnessed the stabbing of a
OL,10,Fheavily pregnant woman before bravely
OL,11,Frunning to help.
OL,13,FAttempted murderer Daniel Popescu had
OL,14,Fbeen waiting for his pregnant ex-
OL,15,Fgirlfriend Andreea Pintili to return
OL,16,Fhome from taking her children to
OL,17,Fschool in Aberfan in December last
OL,18,Fyear.
