OL,7,FCrouched behind a vehicle with a seven
OL,8,Fto eight-inch knife in his hand, he
OL,9,Fwaited for her until she arrived home,
OL,10,Fbefore grabbing her by the arm, at
OL,11,Fwhich point she attempted to run away
OL,12,Fbut fell to the ground. Popescu then
OL,13,Fstabbed her a number of times.
OL,15,FMiss Pintili, who was 37 weeks
OL,16,Fpregnant at the time, described
OL,17,Fholding her stomach and trying to
OL,18,Fprotect her unborn child.
