OL,7,FA woman who had been passing with her
OL,8,Fdog screamed and ran to try and help,
OL,9,Fwhich caused Popescu to run off.
OL,11,FAfter Popescu was jailed for 17 years
OL,12,Fand four months after pleading guilty
OL,13,Fto attempted murder and a stalking
OL,14,Foffence, police have released footage
OL,15,Fof the moments leading up to the
OL,16,Fvicious attack.
