OL,7,FCrown Court heard how Popescu and Miss
OL,8,FPintili had split up around August
OL,9,F2023 after Popescu developed a
OL,10,Fgambling habit. He then became
OL,11,Fobsessed with her.
OL,13,FOn the day of the attack, was brought
OL,14,Fto a standstill with schools locked
OL,15,Fdown while armed police searched for
OL,16,Fthe knifeman who had fled the scene.
OL,18,FMiss Pintili was taken to the
OL,19,FUniversity Hospital of Wales in
OL,20,FCardiff with stab wounds to her back
OL,21,Fand thumb.
