OL,7,FShe received treatment and was
OL,8,Fdischarged the following day. Her baby
OL,9,Fdid not sustain any injuries and was
OL,10,Fborn soon after the attack.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector James Morris said:
OL,13,F"Daniel Popescu armed himself with a
OL,14,Fknife and lay in wait for his victim
OL,15,Fbefore launching a senseless and
OL,16,Fsustained act of violence in the
OL,17,Fmiddle of the street. I can only
OL,18,Fimagine the fear she must have felt
OL,19,Fand the impact this disturbing
OL,20,Fincident has had on her.
