OL,3,CChilling screams of brave dog-walker
OL,4,Cwho rushed to help stabbed pregnant
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,F"It is clear from the sheer vicious
OL,8,Fand sustained force he used that his
OL,9,Fintention was to kill her.
OL,11,F"The strength and bravery of the
OL,12,Fvictim in supporting this prosecution
OL,13,Fhas been extraordinary. Unsurprisingly
OL,14,Fshe remains psychologically scarred as
OL,15,Fa result of the incident, but I know
OL,16,Fthat, thanks to her courage, Daniel
OL,17,FPopescu will be unable to harm any
OL,18,Ffurther women. I hope that today's
OL,19,Fsentence will bring at least a degree
OL,20,Fof closure for her.
